Package com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.dispatching

Class RuntimeSupervisor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.dispatching.RuntimeSupervisor
  • public class RuntimeSupervisor
extends Object
    Supervisor that creates and stores InteractionRuntimes. This supervisor will create a new RuntimeSupervisor.InteractionRuntime for every command execution with a TTL of 15 minutes.
    Since:
    4.0.0
    Version:
    4.0.0
    Author:
    Kaktushose
